title: Assistant DJ? (w/ Pete Correale & Tracey Carnazzo)
description: In defense of Grape Nuts, Jacob goes head to head with Jay and Dan over his favorite cereal. Pete Correale discusses getting high before a show and the weirdness of driving home alone right after one. Turns out DJ Lou is actually DJ Assistant & Tracey Carnazzo talks about falling in love and leaving NYC for the hills of West Virginia
